item.title: The Air by crazybaby (NANO) is now offered in 10 different colors
item.description:
Source: Hwee Seng Electronics. Air by crazybaby (NANO) is available in 10 colours. Hwee Seng Electronics, a Singaporean distributor specializing in audio electronics, has become the official distributor for Crazybaby, a provider of high-quality audio devices. Their product, Air by crazybaby (NANO), also called Nano, is now available in Singapore through Hwee Seng Electronics. Nano earbuds combine Crazybaby’s modern and stylish look with a water-resistant build. These earbuds utilize carbon nanotube technology, which produces sound differently than traditional methods and generally doesn’t need moving parts...
